Source: https://github.com/libretro/slang-shaders/tree/master/crt
        (crt-guest-advanced-fast.slangp + shaders/guest/fast/*.slang
         + shaders/guest/advanced/lut/*.png)

Bundled in vibenes with the .slangp's relative paths rewritten so the
chain is self-contained inside this directory. The shader sources and
LUT PNGs are otherwise identical to upstream. Unused variant files
(perf-pass / pre-shadersf / linearizef / crt-guest-advanced-pass1f /
crt-guest-advanced-pass2f) are not bundled - they belong to the
"fastest" sibling preset which we don't ship.
